</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-fUklNj thmnJ pf-98_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-100_">Consult a professional

</span></h2><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Consult_a_professional_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1686676857" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Consult_a_professional_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1686676857 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Consult_a_professional_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1686676857 320w" width="1966" height="1311" alt="Consult a professional - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " title="Consult a professional - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gtJxSR jkHSry pf-101_"/><p class="sc-eONOlN cfGtgs pf-102_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-104_">If you have an underlying medical condition such as heart disease or diabetes, it's essential to consult with a healthcare professional before undertaking strenuous summer workouts. A healthcare provider can provide personalised advice based on your specific needs and circumstances.

</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-fUklNj thmnJ pf-105_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-107_">Key points to remember
